🌳 Recommended Branch Structure

main (or master):
Stable production-ready code
Only merge tested, reviewed code here. Tagged for releases.

develop
Integration branch for ongoing development
Features and fixes are merged here before going to main.

feature/*
Individual features or enhancements
Create from develop, work on the feature, then merge back into develop.

bugfix/*
Fixes for non-critical issues
Same workflow as features, but focused on bug resolution.

release/*
Pre-release stabilization
Branch off develop when preparing a release. Only bug fixes and documentation updates allowed.

hotfix/*
Urgent fixes for production
Branch off main, fix the issue, merge into both main and develop.

